i\" />"},{"pid":"2f7a3ce62b665f1cd893782b241c43a574ea5cc6","tid":345670,"uid":4635,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T09:51:57.000Z","msg":"薄荷味"},{"pid":"20ce527f99050e40c0168bf9ba89aeda0b10fef4","tid":345670,"uid":16046,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T09:53:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>薄荷味</blockquote><br />\n我搵唔返 邊到仲有賣 <br />\n其實除左青蘋果同橙 其他都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aff8e47b9e384ab3af72449efb8b71fbfa2ab54b","tid":345670,"uid":66759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T09:53:49.000Z","msg":"薄荷"},{"pid":"e809ed85b494227957c4e6f0f0787ad2d00b3a74","tid":345670,"uid":106307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T10:10:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我覺得係白兔糖 不過以前同而家個隻唔同味咁 細細個食個隻好香牛奶味唔太甜,而家食個d冇牛奶香而且得個死甜 a貨咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自從之前有單新聞話白兔糖乜乜柒柒之後就好少食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過我之前都好鐘意食 好鐘意啲糖痴牙嘅感覺<br />\n雖然你離左題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有感而發 返回正題先 我都鐘意士多啤梨味 最好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c143b93b06dcace6361f8ebe41619c7e2add5fd","tid":345670,"uid":2485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T10:11:51.000Z","msg":"薄荷盒裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n記得細個想玩個盒所以叫屋企人買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bc67da5777fb25e765e2207e3b0ae03870472c6","tid":345670,"uid":119379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T10:27:11.000Z","msg":"瑞士糖既話，我會揀橙味<br />\n<br />\n以前返支那買過朱古力味，都係鍾意水果味多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\